notes:

Above level 12 bards train at library in Parth.

The asterisk denotes that another higher level monster also drops the item.

The order of items and skills has been changed (luck was moved): 

level    instructor		skills in order

2 3 4    minstrel 	   	riding, luck, geology
5 6 7  	 muse 			math, acrobatics, navigation
8 9 10	 bard 			alchemy, time-keeping, strategy
11, 12	 master bard 		poetry, music




